snippet.title: Super Robot Wars W - Valguard All Attacks (English Subs)
snippet.description: The combination between Valhawk and Valguard. It's a powerful and huge Super Robot, and the good thing is that we get to use it soon in the game. Valguard looks a little like SRX with the design and with some attacks, but I still think SRX is better than Valguard.
